                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For the text of proposals presented on April 15 by the United Nations Commission
                    for India and Pakistan to the Governments of India and Pakistan for
                    implementation of the Commission’s resolution of August 13, 1948, and for
                    related documentation, see <gloss target="#t_SC1">SC</gloss>, <hi rend="italic">4th yr. Special Suppl, No. 7</hi>, pages 102 ff.</p>
